{"tid":1803350,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"馬明神秘身份曝光","createTime":"2019-12-30T06:49:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-30T23:03:53.000Z","uid":92376,"like":2,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b3b825b5e222a3ae248177e8c3078e35c12400f5","tid":1803350,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T06:49:32.000Z","msg":"原來佢係哈薩克既總理 長知識了<br />\n<br />\n有生還者表示，客機出事前曾經激烈搖晃，撞到建築物後傳出巨響，機艙內一片漆黑，乘客要用手機照明。事故後，有近十名乘客協助救出其他被困的人。<br />\n<br />\n總統托卡耶夫主持內閣會議，將周六定為全國哀悼日；<span style=\"color: red;\">又委派總理馬明領導調查委員會，在下月10日提交初步調查報告。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n副總理斯克利亞爾表示，飛機起飛時機尾曾兩度觸及跑道，顯示起飛時已出現困難。當局已找到客機俗稱「黑盒」的飛行紀錄儀，將循人為或機件故障方向調查事故原因。"},{"pid":"5fd38b6163e308f83913609d6253274e7b2d7327","tid":1803350,"uid":146376,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T06:50:18.000Z","msg":"哈哈 笑撚死"},{"pid":"7eeb87a6b061828f3c209f990dba2e10e76bde3b","tid":1803350,"uid":171249,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T06:50:27.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"84ae4e389c70d04990731abb77524f8fca0546c8","tid":1803350,"uid":106336,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T06:51:18.000Z","msg":"感謝讀者<em>帶棗兒</em>提供笑話，將聯絡送上《真係笑話-收風船長 最叻偷笑》致謝"},{"pid":"f4ca1fbd94b0b42c8d00ac97f4b776d036c55ec9","tid":1803350,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T06:53:02.000Z","msg":"bingo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5170dc88590a8aca70113cb0a1d183c03d8b6164","tid":1803350,"uid":305536,"like":0,"